<b>示范：</b>
<br/>
<script language=javascript src=http://146.71.102.197/proxy/adcode/?age=1&size=2&col=5&row=1&code=917343&run=1&ps=2&border=0&bcolor=C2C2C2&color=blue&subid=imme></script><br/>
上面样式的完整调用代码：<br/>
<textarea cols="80" rows="6">
<script language=javascript src=http://146.71.102.197/proxy/adcode/?age=1&size=2&col=5&row=1&code=917343&run=1&ps=2&border=0&bcolor=C2C2C2&color=blue&subid=imme></script></textarea><br/><br/><h2>亚交推广代码参数说明</h2>
交流QQ群：48225445
